{"tid":675450,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[沉重哀悼]陳百祥逝世","createTime":"2018-05-23T13:44:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T15:58:03.000Z","uid":37380,"like":18,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e249d46e562a5c0bb08bb584c73f9a232673e050","tid":675450,"uid":37380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T13:44:01.000Z","msg":"2017-06-06<br />\n訃聞<br />\n香港精武體育會 主席陳百祥先生不幸於公歷二零一七年五月十九日逝世，享年八十有四。<br />\n陳百祥先生生前服務香港精武體育會超過五十年，貢獻良多，深得會員愛戴。今溘然辭世，本會同人深感惋惜。陳百祥先生遺體奉移香港殯儀館治喪，謹擇公歷六月十日（星期六）下午六時設靈於一樓主澤堂，翌日 十一（星期日）上午九時半大殮，十一時辭靈，隨即出殯，奉柩歌連臣角場火化，謹此 奉 聞 香港精武體育會 謹啟 <br />\n<br />\n香港精武體育會仝人 泣告<br />\n<br />\n治喪處：香港殯儀館<br />\n地址：英皇道六七九號<br />\n電話：二五六三 零二四一<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinwoo.com.hk/load.php?id=303619&amp;p_link_id=140908\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinwoo.com.hk%2Fload.php%3Fid%3D303619%26p_link_id%3D140908&d=KczRiGhJ2dbuiXOhhANADW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=80a89cf9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinwoo.com.hk/load.php?id=303619&amp;p_link_id=140908</a>"},{"pid":"6f2f4796e8466d617d76d514ece4f433ac1e2c0c","tid":675450,"uid":37380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T13:44:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8996cc2e6af6f3c3bfc4188a3dcb6ff6f26a01d1","tid":675450,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T13:45:43.000Z","msg":"2017-06-06<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3da4ffcac5c3a78fb20f03d999cac8b89001431","tid":675450,"uid":37380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8996cc2e6af6f3c3bfc4188a3dcb6ff6f26a01d1","tid":675450,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T13:45:43.000Z","msg":"2017-06-06<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T14:02:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"